{
  "stem": "22728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it's been over 50 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's been 55 years, so the horror kind of pales, and you tend to sweep it aside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not that I haven't been active in anything I can get my hands on, pretty much, for Jewish causes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm proud of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I really went to work at Jewish Family Service, and I was there every day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I took it real seriously, for six years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then, you know, you know when it's enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think when it becomes a burden, you should go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Let somebody else do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's what happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know exactly what that was about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] What people were doing to each other in Europe, man's inhumanity towards his fellow man-- I was old enough to understand those things, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] knowing that America could have ended the war sooner and saved a lot of people, knowing that they were turned away from America.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] broadcasts were called-- what were they called?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Free France-- Free France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all you can do-- you are unable to do anything about it, but you can be angry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was there anything else you wanted to say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I feel very fortunate that I escaped like that and built a wonderful family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have eight grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have no discord in our family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I met this incredible guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents said, we don't marry Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the welcome for Boris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on his mustering out-pay and my last flight ticket from United, we went to New York and got married in a snow storm.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody said a word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody said that that's not going to last, because we were very different people, and here we are.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
